# Lake build artefacts + downloaded Mathlib oleans. Idiomatic Lean 4
# layout — see https://lean-lang.org/lean4/doc/setup.html. The CI
# workflow `formal-verification.yml` regenerates this directory via
# `leanprover/lean-action@v1` (Mathlib cache fetch + `lake build`).
.lake/
build/
*.olean
*.ilean
*.trace
